casebody.data:
Thursday, April 10, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

94-1777. State v. Dunlap.

Hamilton App. No. C-930121. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s emergency motion to transfer appellant from Idaho Maximum Security Institution in Idaho to the Mansfield Correctional Institution in Mansfield, Ohio. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the emergency motion to transfer appellant be, and hereby is, denied.
